sentence.text: Herein, we designed a retro-inverso isomer of <sup>L</sup>c(cell-cell signaling-1), termed <sup>D</sup>c(LyP-1), expecting to inspire brain metastatic tumor targeted drug delivery.
Further, <sup>L</sup>c(cell-cell signaling-1) modified PEG-PLA micelles displayed much higher in vivo distribution in brain metastatic tumor than <sup>D</sup>c(LyP-1).
All results suggested that <sup>L</sup>c(cell-cell signaling-1) had a better performance than <sup>D</sup>c(LyP-1) in brain metastatic tumor-targeted drug delivery
